lead_paragraph: Kentucky achieved one goal with a dominant performance against LSU on Saturday that made the 22nd-ranked Wildcats confident of attaining another in the Southeastern Conference Tournament.

headline.print_headline: No. 22 Kentucky Dominates LSU 94-77 in Regular-Season Finale
